    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, i've tried everything. therapy, books, trying to change my habits... it's like my brain is wired to fail. it's not even a mistake anymore, it's just how i'm built. the loop is too big to break. it's like gravity, it just pulls me back down every single time. i just can't stop it. it feels like the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... make it stop for good.",
